{"page":10,"width":1198,"height":1676,"lines":[{"text":"The next day, two men caught","confidence":96.6,"x":0.5217,"y":0.10859,"width":0.37479,"height":0.0179},{"text":"the lion with a large net. The","confidence":96.3,"x":0.5217,"y":0.13783,"width":0.35559,"height":0.0185},{"text":"lion bit the net with his sharp","confidence":96.5,"x":0.52337,"y":0.16706,"width":0.35643,"height":0.0185},{"text":"AY","confidence":66.8,"x":0.24374,"y":0.16885,"width":0.01669,"height":0.01193},{"text":"teeth, but that did not help.","confidence":96.4,"x":0.5217,"y":0.1957,"width":0.3414,"height":0.01909},{"text":"How can I get out? asked","confidence":94.4,"x":0.52504,"y":0.22494,"width":0.33222,"height":0.0185},{"text":"the lion sadly.","confidence":96.5,"x":0.5217,"y":0.25418,"width":0.17112,"height":0.0185},{"text":"Just then, the mouse saw the","confidence":96.0,"x":0.11603,"y":0.30609,"width":0.35309,"height":0.01671},{"text":"lion. I can help you, he said.","confidence":95.0,"x":0.1177,"y":0.33473,"width":0.36811,"height":0.0185},{"text":"Dial","confidence":44.6,"x":0.63773,"y":0.34308,"width":0.05509,"height":0.01671},{"text":"Soon, the mouse made a big","confidence":96.4,"x":0.11686,"y":0.36217,"width":0.34558,"height":0.02267},{"text":"hole in the net with his teeth.","confidence":96.6,"x":0.1177,"y":0.3932,"width":0.35726,"height":0.01492},{"text":"The lion got out. Thank you!","confidence":96.4,"x":0.11603,"y":0.42303,"width":0.37813,"height":0.0179},{"text":"said the lion happily.","confidence":95.7,"x":0.11686,"y":0.45167,"width":0.25626,"height":0.0185},{"text":"From then on, the lion and the mouse became friends.","confidence":95.6,"x":0.18698,"y":0.50955,"width":0.65943,"height":0.0173},{"text":"weak","confidence":96.5,"x":0.67947,"y":0.89916,"width":0.06594,"height":0.01492},{"text":"strong","confidence":96.9,"x":0.26377,"y":0.90155,"width":0.07596,"height":0.01611}]}